{"tid":1693912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"法思想家霍爾巴赫：有自由的地方就是家園","createTime":"2019-11-05T01:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T16:10:59.000Z","uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c5f735d6109629221edab74c061351556244b1a","tid":1693912,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:07:15.000Z","msg":"法思想家霍爾巴赫：有自由的地方就是家園<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/diva/art/oneminreading/21201?sort=dsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fdiva%2Fart%2Foneminreading%2F21201%3Fsort%3Ddsc&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=b406de08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/diva/art/oneminreading/21201?sort=dsc</a>"},{"pid":"5eb4df66705839f6ed0dcf71f4ce710fc6821d9b","tid":1693912,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T20:06:28.000Z","msg":"港警是不是香港人？還是中國人？<br />\n<br />\n我是台灣人，看過近5個月的香港直播，各種黑警逮人的鏡頭都看過。<br />\n至於黑警強暴、殺人的影像，老實說，網上沒有。<br />\n港警粗暴捕人的影像，在英國（北愛爾蘭）、西班牙（加泰隆尼亞）和智利都很常見。<br />\n所以，香港被捕越多．遊行的人數越來越少。連習近平都稱讚林鄭月娥。<br />\n姑且不論連習近平和林鄭月娥是不是香港人？<br />\n簡單的問題：港警是不是香港人？<br />\n「是」：正評<br />\n「不是」：負評"},{"pid":"40aca833d2026bfa56d349bd15f26d2e6f47d449","tid":1693912,"uid":271530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5f735d6109629221edab74c061351556244b1a","tid":1693912,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:07:15.000Z","msg":"法思想家霍爾巴赫：有自由的地方就是家園<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/diva/art/oneminreading/21201?sort=dsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fdiva%2Fart%2Foneminreading%2F21201%3Fsort%3Ddsc&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=b406de08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/diva/art/oneminreading/21201?sort=dsc</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"你願意為該地的自由拋頭顱灑熱血的地方就是家園"},{"pid":"91f21af5ec43c55d13c04c12b1e9ee874315630a","tid":1693912,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40aca833d2026bfa56d349bd15f26d2e6f47d449","tid":1693912,"uid":271530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c5f735d6109629221edab74c061351556244b1a","tid":1693912,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:07:15.000Z","msg":"法思想家霍爾巴赫：有自由的地方就是家園<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/diva/art/oneminreading/21201?sort=dsc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fdiva%2Fart%2Foneminreading%2F21201%3Fsort%3Ddsc&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=b406de08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/diva/art/oneminreading/21201?sort=dsc</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"你願意為該地的自由拋頭顱灑熱血的地方就是家園"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T16:10:59.000Z","msg":"right"}]}